            [
                "speak",
                [
                    "Jamke",
                    "Come on, Aideen!{br}Take the brat and get out of here, and quickly!{w}{br}You need to get as far away as you can before Gandolf finds out!{w}",
                    "",
                    "",
                    "noir"
